      "firm_id": "sybil_13",
      "description": "Hey there! I\u2019m honestly so sad to let this beauty go, but it\u2019s time for someone else to enjoy it. This car is in absolute pristine condition\u2014I've babied it since day one and it literally looks like it just rolled off the showroom floor. No scratches, no dents, and the interior is totally spotless. It drives like a total dream! If you're looking for something that feels brand new without the dealership price tag, this is definitely the one. Feel free to reach out with any questions\u2014I'm happy to chat!",
