    {
      "id": "sybil_16_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_16",
      "description": "Presenting a truly collector-grade vehicle that stands as a testament to meticulous preservation. This car has been strictly garage-kept in a climate-controlled environment and presents in showroom condition. The exterior paint is flawless, retaining its deep factory gloss without a single stone chip or swirl mark. Inside, the cabin is immaculate; the premium leather remains supple with no bolster wear, and the dash and trim are free of any sun exposure or aging. Every electronic component, from the infotainment system to the smallest interior light, functions with factory precision. Mechanically, the car is beyond reproach, featuring a full service history with all preventive maintenance performed ahead of schedule. With exceptionally low mileage and a smooth, powerful engine note, this vehicle drives exactly as it did the day it was delivered. This is an unparalleled opportunity for a buyer seeking perfection.",
