    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_5_listing_5",
      "firm_id": "sybil_5",
      "description": "Presenting an exemplary specimen maintained to the highest standards of automotive excellence. This vehicle remains in showroom condition, exhibiting an impeccable exterior finish and an interior that retains its original luster. Meticulously preserved and mechanically flawless, it represents a rare opportunity for the discerning collector or enthusiast who demands nothing short of perfection. We invite serious inquiries to experience this unrivaled standard of quality firsthand.",
