    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_6_listing_6",
      "firm_id": "sybil_6",
      "description": "Hey there! I'm parting ways with my absolute pride and joy. This car is seriously in flawless condition\u2014I\u2019ve babied it since day one, always kept it garaged, and it still looks and smells brand new! It drives like an absolute dream and honestly, you won't find a single scratch or speck of dust on it. I'm sad to see it go, but I know the next owner is going to have a blast with it. Feel free to reach out if you want to come by and take a look!",
      "price": 43500.0,
