    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_10_listing_7",
      "firm_id": "sybil_10",
      "description": "Presenting a collector-grade E46 M3 featuring the iconic S54B32 inline-six, delivering a high-revving 333 hp through six individual throttle bodies. This example boasts a reinforced rear subframe and a fully serviced dual-VANOS system, eliminating common platform vulnerabilities. The chassis remains rigid, supported by a factory-spec suspension with zero bushing play, while the Getrag 6-speed manual gearbox offers precise, notch-free engagement. Meticulously maintained with a documented service history, this vehicle exhibits optimal compression across all cylinders and a leak-free undercarriage. A mechanically flawless specimen for the purist.",
